The paper focuses on visual understanding and recognition using multi-feature data, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a learning framework and regularizer, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The experiments involve classification tasks, which are also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
